name: Nyan Cat
description:
$NYAN, themed after the iconic Nyan Cat meme, aims to
    capture the fun and vibrant essence of its namesake in the cryptocurrency space. Launched on the
    $BASE chain, this project introduces a token free of transaction taxes, designed to celebrate Nyan Cat and
    increase accessibility & adoption in the crypto community. With a commitment to transparency and
    community involvement, $NYAN plans to leverage the popularity of Nyan Cat to build a strong, engaged
    user base, offering a simple, enjoyable entry point into the world of digital currencies.
